com.sun.messaging

Interface PropertyOwner


  • public interface PropertyOwner
    The PropertyOwner interface is implemented by any property that owns other properties. The property type of this property is com.sun.messaging.PropertyOwner.

    Setting a property Type to com.sun.messaging.PropertyOwner indicates that dependant property information can be obtained from the class via the interface methods described below.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getPropertyDefault(String propname)
      Returns the default value of a single owned property.
      String getPropertyLabel(String propname)
      Returns the label of a single owned property.
      String[] getPropertyNames()
      Returns a String array of property names that this PropertyOwner owns.
      String getPropertyType(String propname)
      Returns the type of a single owned property.
